reviews.text:
Great recipe, i love it! The best Almond Milk i vaped so far.&#xD;
After 9 days of steeping, it really a excellent, full milk flavour. &#xD;
On exhale the Almond is coming out and playing so well with the Vanilla and the creamy milk flavour.&#xD;
Good balance of flavours. I have add 0.4%  Cap Super Sweet because iam a sweet tooth :-)&#xD;
Thanks for the recipe, good job.
